Chapter Z. Databases

z.1. MariaDB

z.1.1. Connect to server
mariadb -h $MARIADB_HOST -u $MARIADB_USER -p $MARIADB_DATABASE

z.1.1. Show databases:
SHOW DATABASES;

z.1.2. Choose a database:
USE databasename;

z.1.3. Show tables (inside database):
SHOW TABLES;

z.2. PostgreSQL

z.2.1. Connect to server:
psql -h $POSTGRES_HOST -U $POSTGRES_USER -W -d $POSTGRES_DATABASE

z.2.2. List database:
\l

z.2.3. Connect to database:
\c databasename

z.2.4. Show relations:
\dt

